Titolo: Visage (video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Visage is an independent psychological horror video game by SadSquare Studio. Set in a strangely-structured house with a somber history, players control Dwayne Anderson as he explores the backstories of the inhabitants that once lived there. Mainly inspired by the cancelled project of P.T., the game ran Kickstarter and Steam Greenlight campaigns. It was later released on October 30, 2020.

Genere: Survival horror

Valutazione: N/A
